title: Bosu Body Bar
typeOfFood: Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Billed as "healthy eating" food bar with a selection of food suitable for vegans. Staff is knowledgeable about what's vegan. Basically, you choose from a base and add sides (except the apple coleslaw) to go with your protein (has tofu). Range of smoothies and juices.
